1 limi ted to a driver license and passport. The name of the spouse
2 listed on the death certificate must match the name on the
3 government issued identification. The banking institution shall
4 make photo or digital copies of the death certificate and the two
5 forms of identification and maintain such copies for their records
6 and shall maintain such records for ten (10) years.
7 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
